{"tid":124464,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【曾蔭權罪成】謝偉俊：服務港多年 唔好過份怪責 不應過份高興","createTime":"2017-02-17T15:27:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-17T21:43:51.000Z","uid":48093,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6efc195fd2d5e551de0367ec352891f3b97636de","tid":124464,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T15:27:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170217/large/1487342954_d0b9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170217%2Flarge%2F1487342954_d0b9.jpg&h=38585826&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n前特首曾蔭權一項藉公職人員行為不當罪成，最高要面對7年牢獄生涯。曾提出彈劾曾蔭權的立法會議員謝偉俊表示，當年已覺得不妥，今日判罪反映任何人都要就做過的事負責任，亦要尊重陪審團的決定，「法律面前人人平等，特首都唔例外」。<br />\n<br />\n謝偉俊又指，曾蔭權雖服務香港多年，也要有應有的懲罰，「但睇在佢服務香港多年，唔好過份怪責佢」，強調任何人被定罪，都不應過份高興。"},{"pid":"aaf9a92e2df88539bdcaa1118bae05e48dd4766e","tid":124464,"uid":43173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T17:20:27.000Z","msg":"曾蔭權7年，689要幾耐？"},{"pid":"32d154ae9508c988edf5f6143bbf89b4f1877b5d","tid":124464,"uid":7369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T17:23:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>曾蔭權7年，689要幾耐？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果條仆街真係做到政協副主席，到時真係咬佢唔入架<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06ac25252597cc00b34a842de559404f571654a8","tid":124464,"uid":16034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T20:10:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>曾蔭權7年，689要幾耐？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果條仆街真係做到政協副主席，到時真係咬佢唔入架<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n刑不上委呢套摺左啦 主要睇佢權鬥有無企岩邊者 唔係周永康呢種政法委書記 入埋常都收皮啦"},{"pid":"5f1fddd4145d9d8a4a4bcbc9ed226999cd6d1637","tid":124464,"uid":37427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T20:53:49.000Z","msg":"到時全家移民外國啦, 佢重會留係呢面咩<br />\n易家都打好哂關係, 到時叫人係呢面幫佢做野<br />\n自己係外國嘆世界"},{"pid":"3b64f3cb41764b9a50b708211f99fecc869f889c","tid":124464,"uid":44925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T21:43:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>曾蔭權7年，689要幾耐？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果條仆街真係做到政協副主席，到時真係咬佢唔入架<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔關事，政協副主席係垃圾掛名位黎，唔好睇得咁重<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最多求情果陣判輕啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}